00:27:01.868 --> 00:27:05.250
Energy given to the electron -
W, because you paid

00:27:05.250 --> 00:27:08.750
W to get it out of the
well, and whatever is left is

00:27:08.750 --> 00:27:10.140
the kinetic energy.
 

00:27:10.140 --> 00:27:13.480
So Einstein predicted photons
from independent arguments,

00:27:13.480 --> 00:27:16.051
and according to him,
light and frequency w is

00:27:16.051 --> 00:27:19.295
made up of particles,
each of which contains energy

00:27:19.295 --> 00:27:21.210
ℏw.
 

00:27:21.210 --> 00:27:23.818
So you can see what's happening.
 

00:27:23.818 --> 00:27:27.738
