00:27:42.578 --> 00:27:46.238
They cannot do it,
but if you send 10 tall,

00:27:46.238 --> 00:27:49.808
powerful people,
they will lift it out.

00:27:49.808 --> 00:27:53.096
So what's happening with light
is that as you crank up the

00:27:53.096 --> 00:27:55.227
w,
even if it's not very bright,

00:27:55.227 --> 00:27:57.952
the individual packets are
carrying more and more energy

00:27:57.952 --> 00:28:01.157
and more and more momentum,
and that's why they succeed in

00:28:01.157 --> 00:28:02.660
