it's ℏw,

00:28:06.836 --> 00:28:09.664
then the kinetic energy of the
electron is the energy you gave

00:28:09.664 --> 00:28:11.602
with 1 photon,
take away the W,

00:28:11.602 --> 00:28:13.759
that's the price you pay to
leave the metal.

00:28:13.759 --> 00:28:16.240
The rest of it is kinetic
energy.

00:28:16.240 --> 00:28:19.319
So when plotted as a function
