00:28:30.800 --> 00:28:32.009
depends on the metal.
 

00:28:32.009 --> 00:28:34.490
And you shine light and you
crank up the frequency,

00:28:34.490 --> 00:28:35.730
till something happens.
 

00:28:35.730 --> 00:28:39.096
And just to be sure,
you go a little beyond that and

00:28:39.096 --> 00:28:42.730
you find that the kinetic energy
grows linearly in w.

00:28:42.730 --> 00:28:46.165
Anyway, this is how one
confirmed the existence,

00:28:46.165 --> 00:28:48.578
indirect existence,
of photons.

00:28:48.578 --> 00:28:52.376
There's another experiment that
