00:29:55.116 --> 00:29:57.412
relativity,
because he said that was a real

00:29:57.412 --> 00:29:57.788
problem.
 

00:29:57.788 --> 00:30:00.288
That's a problem I couldn't
track.

00:30:00.288 --> 00:30:03.942
Now it turns out that even till
the end, he didn't find an

00:30:03.942 --> 00:30:06.380
answer that was satisfactory to
him.

00:30:06.380 --> 00:30:08.317
The answer I'm giving you
certainly works,

00:30:08.317 --> 00:30:10.920
makes all the predictions,
never said anything wrong.

00:30:10.920 --> 00:30:15.087
Until something better comes to
