00:30:15.087 --> 00:30:15.430
it.
 

00:30:15.430 --> 00:30:18.550
Anyway, going back,
the second experiment that

00:30:18.550 --> 00:30:20.980
confirmed the reality of
photons.

00:30:20.980 --> 00:30:24.063
See, if you say light is made
of particles and each one has an

00:30:24.063 --> 00:30:26.337
energy and momentum,
do you understand why the

00:30:26.337 --> 00:30:28.359
photoelectric effect is a good
test.

00:30:28.359 --> 00:30:30.339
It agrees with that picture.
 

00:30:30.339 --> 00:30:31.808
Individual particles come.
 

00:30:31.808 --> 00:30:34.929
Some have the energy to
liberate the electron and some

00:30:34.929 --> 00:30:35.400
don't.
 

00:30:35.400 --> 00:30:37.509
And if individually,
they cannot do it,

00:30:37.509 --> 00:30:39.618
it doesn't matter how many you
