00:30:39.618 --> 00:30:43.107
Now you may have thought of one
scenario in which all of these

00:30:43.107 --> 00:30:46.025
tiny little kids can get
something lifted out of the

00:30:46.025 --> 00:30:46.539
well.
 

00:30:46.539 --> 00:30:51.750
How will they do that?
 

00:30:51.750 --> 00:30:55.246
Maybe 10 kids together,
