accuracy.

00:55:38.690 --> 00:55:40.420
I dare you to make it.
 

00:55:40.420 --> 00:55:45.018
In Newtonian mechanics,
that's not a big deal.

00:55:45.018 --> 00:55:48.480
So let's say this is the
y direction,

00:55:48.480 --> 00:55:52.710
and you say,
"I'll give you an electron

00:55:52.710 --> 00:55:56.349
