00:56:31.518 --> 00:56:33.809
I can make my filter finer and
finer and finer,

00:56:33.809 --> 00:56:36.378
till I'm able to give the
electrons a perfectly well

00:56:36.378 --> 00:56:39.199
defined position and perfectly
well defined momentum,

00:56:39.199 --> 00:56:41.289
