01:11:49.546 --> 01:11:52.460
probability the electron will
end up somewhere.

01:11:52.460 --> 01:11:55.673
And also, in a double slit
experiment, it is no longer

01:11:55.673 --> 01:11:59.069
possible to think that the
electron went through one slit

01:11:59.069 --> 01:11:59.979
