the numbers should be additive.

01:12:05.819 --> 01:12:08.877
The fact they are not means an
electron knows how many slits

01:12:08.877 --> 01:12:12.091
are open, and only a wave knows
how many slits are open because

01:12:12.091 --> 01:12:13.439
it's going everywhere.
 

01:12:13.439 --> 01:12:16.479
A particle can only look at one
slit at a time.

01:12:16.479 --> 01:12:19.594
In fact, it doesn't know
